050900/
051000******************************************************************
051100*                   INICIALIZACAO                                *
051200******************************************************************
051300*
051400 010-E-INICIO.
051500
051600
051700
051800     MOVE    ATTRIBUTE NAME OF ATTRIBUTE EXCEPTIONTASK
051900                            OF ATTRIBUTE EXCEPTIONTASK OF MYSELF
052000                            TO LINKTOCOMS.
052100
052200
052300     CHANGE  ATTRIBUTE TITLE OF "DCILIBRARY" TO LINKTOCOMS.
052400
052500
