053800       ON    EXCEPTION
053900             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T432/DB : OPEN ERROR TDBDETRAN"
054000             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU    140-S-ERRODB
054100             CALL    SYSTEM          DMTERMINATE.
054200
054300
054400
054500
054600
054700
