055400******************************************************************
055500*
055600 020-E-PROCESSA.
055700
055800
055900
056000     MOVE    SPACES                  TO      AREA-IN
056100                                             AREA-OUT.
056200
056300     RECEIVE COMS-IN MESSAGE         INTO    AREA-IN.
056400
056500     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       00 OR 89 OR 92 OR
056600                                             93 OR 97
056700             NEXT    SENTENCE
056800     ELSE
