057900                                     USING   USER-DESG
058000                                             USER-NAME
058100                                     GIVING  USER-FLAG.
058200
058300
058400
058500     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-NOTFOUND.
058600
058700     ACCEPT  AX-DATA-MAQ             FROM    DATE YYYYMMDD.
058800
058900     IF      IN-CODE                 =       "V432"
059000             PERFORM 030-E-V432      THRU    030-S-V432
059100     ELSE
059200             MOVE    239             TO      IA1.
059300
059400
059500     MOVE    176                     TO      AX-LENGTH.
059600
059700     PERFORM 120-E-MSGOUT            THRU    120-S-MSGOUT.
